    "Brazil's experience is illustrative.",
    "In 2020, lawmakers introduced Bill No.",
    "2630, dubbed the \"Fake News Bill, \" to address online misinformation and abuse.",
    "After delays, the bill regained momentum in 2023 with significant revisions.",
    "The far-reaching proposal would overhaul internet liability rules by establishing new \"duty of care\" obligations for tech platforms regarding content moderation (Freedom House, 2023)."
